question: What fast food restaurant can I find as I progress towards Allen Park Civic Arena, Allen Park, MI from Sea Life Aquarium, Auburn Hills, MI, within a radius of 170 kilometers?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-83.296505 42.70361)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-83.211376 42.258691)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'fast_food'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-83.296505 42.70361)',4326)::geography, 170000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-83.296505 42.70361)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);

answers.poi_name: Hot Dog Tony's Restaurant and Bar

[3].display_name: Sea Life Aquarium, Auburn Hills, MI

[4].display_name: Allen Park Civic Arena, Allen Park, MI
